        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Zone balancing in multi-zone systems</strong><p>For Formby properties with separate upstairs and downstairs zones, TRVs work alongside the zone thermostats to provide individual radiator control within each zone. Combined with smart zone controls, this delivers the most efficient heating setup for a large Formby home.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>From £50 per valve. One radiator left without for bypass.</strong><p>One radiator, usually in the hallway, must be left without a TRV to act as a system bypass. We always advise on this for Formby properties. In a large multi-zone system, the bypass location matters for the system pressure and pump performance.</p></div></div>
      </div>
