      <p class="pf-sub">Free fixed-price quotes. Correct sizing before any recommendation. System balanced. Our own Gas Safe engineers. All Formby L37 postcodes.</p>
      <div class="pf-why-grid">
        <div class="pf-why-item"><h3>Free Quotes. Not Charged.</h3><p>We do not charge for quote visits. Tower Heating, the dominant Formby competitor, charges for quotes. Our quote visits are free and the written price you receive is fixed, the price quoted is the price on the invoice.</p></div>
        <div class="pf-why-item"><h3>BTU Calculation Before Any Recommendation</h3><p>We calculate the correct BTU output for every Formby room before recommending a radiator size. No recommendation based on what was there before or what fits the wall. The room gets the right amount of heat or we do not proceed.</p></div>
        <div class="pf-why-item"><h3>Column and Period Radiator Expertise</h3><p>We specify column radiators correctly for Formby period rooms, the right height, the right column configuration, the right BTU output for the specific room. Not just the radiator that looks right, but the radiator that also heats the room correctly.</p></div>
        <div class="pf-why-item"><h3>System Balanced on Completion</h3><p>Every Formby radiator job includes a full system balance. For multi-zone properties, each zone is balanced individually. Without balancing, a new radiator in a large Formby system affects the performance of other radiators across both zones.</p></div>
        <div class="pf-why-item"><h3>Our Own Gas Safe Engineers</h3><p>All radiator work connecting to the central heating circuit is carried out by our own directly employed Gas Safe registered engineers. Never a sub-contractor. Verify at gassaferegister.co.uk.</p></div>
